OL,3,C'I would have probably punched' Ofsted
OL,4,Cstaff, says education secretary
OL,6,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,7,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,8,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,9,Fhighest rating to its lowest over
OL,10,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,12,FIn December, a coroner concluded the
OL,13,FOfsted inspection on November 15-16 in
OL,14,F2022 "likely contributed" to Mrs
OL,15,FPerry's death.
OL,17,FSir Martyn launched the watchdog's
OL,18,F"Big Listen" public consultation on
OL,19,FFriday which will seek views about
OL,20,FOfsted.
