OL,6,FSir Martyn added: "Ruth's death was a
OL,7,Ftragedy and I am determined to do
OL,8,Feverything that I can to prevent such
OL,9,Ftragedies happening in the future.
OL,11,F"It should never happen again and no
OL,12,Fone should ever feel as Ruth did." The
OL,13,FOfsted chief pledged that "real
OL,14,Faction" would follow the Big Listen.
OL,16,FHis comments came after Professor
OL,17,FJulia Waters, sister of Ruth Perry,
OL,18,Fsaid Ofsted needed to make a "big
OL,19,Fchange" or its consultation would be a
OL,20,F"big waste of time".
